	<h2 id="key-takeaways">Key takeaways</h2>
	<p>
		Efficient page and interaction design ensures fast, reliable access to content in low-resource environments by reducing unnecessary complexity and prioritising essential functionality. These practices improve accessibility, reduce data consumption, and enhance the user experience worldwide.
	</p>

